snippet.title: The War Within - You Must Prepare
snippet.description:
The War Within is coming this November. Are you prepared, Tenno? 

Visit http://warframe.com/thewarwithin for info on how to get ready. 

Heads up, you'll want to make sure you've completed The Second Dream quest as well as the Pluto-Sedna Junction! 

Thanks to the following Warframe players who -- as seen in this video -- are ready and waiting for this massive update:
